ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>切左係咪真係會易病好多？<br />\n我本身扁桃線比正常人大，一年起碼發3次炎，等緊公立排期做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又冇乜關係 不過會冇哂鼻寒"},{"pid":"1b488f2c61218aeb18bbf64cd92e1de568a3bfaa","tid":27940,"uid":23218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中二做左 訓左一晚就出院 <br />\n要睇嗰醫生手勢好唔好 嗰時做 比佢搞到啲瘀血入曬氣管 唔係好抖到氣 食唔到固體野 講野都冇乜聲 番到屋企第二日訓訓下教嘔左粒乒乓波咁大嘅瘀血出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋做手術嗰時比個醫生扯爆左我嘴角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  麻醉一過就痛到喊出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解得我一個要訓咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做完第一晚嘔血同嘔痰 嚇到仆街"},{"pid":"3cfea24fb3780b4d17f645042df716d476017326","tid":27940,"uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"其實呢個手術係睇醫生手勢<br />\n<br />\n手勢好的話第二日已經無乜唔舒服，我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：割過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9059d5016bf5ee76611be031580af2808ca5ff58","tid":27940,"uid":56168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢個手術係睇醫生手勢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手勢好的話第二日已經無乜唔舒服，我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..用咩方法做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：割過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6019859f01f310493f796cdba42d617f565e6e94","tid":27940,"uid":56168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢個手術係睇醫生手勢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手勢好的話第二日已經無乜唔舒服，我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/fac